<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/dft-operator-limited> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "DfT Operator Limited (DFTO) is the government’s public sector rail owning group. DFTO’s purpose is to bring all currently privately-owned train operators into public ownership in advance of the creation of Great British Railways in 2027. DFTO is a public corporation of the Department for Transport ."@en .
